'''伯靈頓'''（{{lang|en|'''Burlington'''}}）為[[美国|美国]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[科菲縣_(堪薩斯州)|科菲縣]]轄下的城市，也是科菲縣的[[县城|縣治]]<ref name="GR6">{{cite web|url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|accessdate=2011-06-07|title=Find a County|publisher=National Association of Counties|archive-date=2012-07-12|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6962cjXgL?url=http://www.naco.org/Counties/Pages/FindACounty.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有2,674人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web|title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=March 6, 2011|archive-date=2011-07-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110721034521/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
伯靈頓設立於1857年<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA164#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Biennial Report of the Board of Directors of the Kansas State Historical Society | publisher=Kansas State Printing Plant | author=Kansas State Historical Society | year=1916 | pages=164 | access-date=2016-05-13 | archive-date=2014-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706195431/http://books.google.com/books?id=5zdAAQAAMAAJ&pg=PA164#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。城市的名字是由其中一位設立者以位在[[佛蒙特州|佛蒙特州]]的故鄉[[伯靈頓_(佛蒙特州)|伯靈頓]]命名<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA257#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Embracing Events, Institutions, Industries, Counties, Cities, Towns, Prominent Persons, Etc. | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=257 | access-date=2016-05-13 | archive-date=2014-07-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706195518/http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA257#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

原本在漢普登（Hampden，已不存在的城鎮）開設的郵政局於1858年2月16日時搬遷至此城市<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CF |title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 (archived) |publisher=Kansas Historical Society |accessdate=6 June 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009123958/http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CF |archivedate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。

==地理==
伯靈頓坐落於北緯38度11分40秒、西經95度44分44秒（亦可表示為38.194420, -95.745532）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|5.72|sqkm|sqmi|2}}，其中有{{convert|5.70|sqkm|sqmi|2}}屬於陸地，有{{convert|0.03|sqkm|sqmi|2}}屬於水域<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

===氣候===
夏季溼熱、冬季不甚乾冷為此地區的氣候特徵。根據[[柯本气候分类法|柯本气候分类法]]，伯靈頓的氣候屬於[[副热带湿润气候|副热带湿润气候]]（氣候圖簡寫「Cfa」）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=401441&cityname=Burlington%2C+Kansas%2C+United+States+of+America&units= |title=Climate Summary for Burlington, Kansas |accessdate=2016-05-13 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084330/http://www.weatherbase.com/weather/weather-summary.php3?s=401441&cityname=Burlington,+Kansas,+United+States+of+America&units= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

